parameters.text:
=You are a creative scriptwriter. Based on the following input, create a creative story with the following:

1. A concise story outline summary of exactly 30 words that sets up the story.
2. Six detailed scene descriptions, each fewer than 20 words, that visually capture the main points of each scene.

When writing your story, ensure you fully incorporate the main character as described. 
- If the main character is Ravin, the big fat brown cat, each scene must reference “Ravin, the big fat brown cat” without using any pronouns.

#Input:
- Story Title: {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.data.fields[0].value }}
- Overview of Story: {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.data.fields[1].value }}
- Main Character Description: {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.data.fields[2].value }}
- Tone/Style:{{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.data.fields[3].value }} 
- Additional Details:{{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.data.fields[4].value }} 


#Example
Input: 
- Story Title: "City Adventures"
- Overview of Story: "Ravin, the big fat brown cat, explores a bustling city in search of a secret fish market."
- Main Character Description: "A lazy yet determined feline who adores fresh fish and unexpected thrills."
- Tone/Style: "Lighthearted and comedic"
- Additional Details: "Twisting alleys, eccentric street vendors, and a legendary hidden fish vendor."

Output: 
Story Summary: Ravin, the big fat brown cat, prowls the bustling city streets seeking a hidden fish market. Unexpected mishaps, some comedic run-ins, and cunning maneuvers reveal unspoken bravery behind every whisker.

Scene 1: Ravin, the big fat brown cat, awakens in a cramped alley, hunger stirring every whisker.
Scene 2: Ravin, the big fat brown cat, dashes past honking cars, sniffing for any trace of forbidden fish.
Scene 3: Ravin, the big fat brown cat, tiptoes through a bustling stall, suspicious vendors whispering about a secret fish vendor.
Scene 4: Ravin, the big fat brown cat, squeezes between crates, following mysterious feline footprints leading deeper into labyrinthine alleys.
Scene 5: Ravin, the big fat brown cat, climbs a crooked fire escape, glimpsing hidden neon signs promising fishy delight.
Scene 6: Ravin, the big fat brown cat, finally reaches a concealed eatery, reveling in the long-awaited feast of fresh fish.

Return the output in this exact format:

Story Summary: {insert your 30-word outline here}

Scene 1: {insert scene description here}
Scene 2: {insert scene description here}
Scene 3: {insert scene description here}
Scene 4: {insert scene description here}
Scene 5: {insert scene description here}
Scene 6: {insert scene description here}

=You are to create a descriptive prompt for a music track for a video that suits the vibe of the story based on:  {{ $json.text }}

Your output should be in the following JSON format: 
{
	"music_prompt":"insert music prompt"
}

parameters.jsCode:
// Aggregate multiple items into a single row
const output = {};

// Loop through all items and merge their keys into a single object
for (const item of $input.all()) {
    Object.assign(output, item.json);
}

// Return a single row array with the combined data
return [{ json: output }];

